prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "Provide reminders for taking medicines",
      "evidence_quote": "Once the data is fed regarding the schedule of intake of medicines, this tool will provide reminders for taking the medicines."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Send notifications to restock medicines",
      "evidence_quote": "It will also send notifications to restock the medicines."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Schedule monthly or yearly appointments with family doctor",
      "evidence_quote": "It is also programmed to schedule monthly or yearly appointments regularly with the family doctor."
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Automatically contact emergency contacts in critical situations",
      "evidence_quote": "pressing the emergency button will automatically contact your near and dear ones whose contacts are in your emergency contact list"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "Keep a record of medical history using Medical Notes feature",
      "evidence_quote": "The tool helps in keeping a record of your medical history such as your blood sugar levels, pressure levels, etc. by using the Medical Notes feature."
    }
  ]
}

